OL,3,CRuling for doctor who removed ovaries
OL,4,Cwithout consent appealed
OL,6,FThe UK's General Medical Council (GMC)
OL,7,Fwill appeal a tribunal decision in the
OL,8,Fcase of a doctor who removed Guernsey
OL,9,Fpatients' ovaries without consent.
OL,11,FDr Ali Shokouh-Amiri, who currently
OL,12,Fpractices at Southend Hospital,
OL,13,Fadmitted to 24 instances of
OL,14,Finappropriate behaviour, out of more
OL,15,Fthan 100 allegations, to the Medical
OL,16,FPractioners Tribunal (MPT).
