OL,3,CRuling for doctor who removed ovaries
OL,4,Cwithout consent appealed
OL,6,FNow, a GMC Panel found that the
OL,7,Ftribunal's determinations of Dr
OL,8,FShokouh Amiri's case appeared to have
OL,9,F"a number of flaws" leading to an
OL,10,Foutcome that was "insufficient to
OL,11,Fprotect the public".
OL,13,FThe Panel acknowledged that the case
OL,14,Fwas "complex" but concluded it was
OL,15,F"very difficult to understand the
OL,16,FMPT's reasoning for reaching their
OL,17,Ffindings".
