OL,3,CRuling for doctor who removed ovaries
OL,4,Cwithout consent appealed
OL,6,FThe GMC also said the MPT was
OL,7,F"dismissive" of patient testimonies,
OL,8,Fadding there were clear examples where
OL,9,Fthe evidence did not support the
OL,10,Ftribunal's findings.
OL,12,FThe appeal will be heard at the High
OL,13,FCourt, with timings to be confirmed.
OL,15,FSix patients were the subject of
OL,16,Fallegations of inappropriate behaviour
OL,17,Frelating to Dr Shokouh-Amiri's work in
OL,18,FGuernsey's Princess Elizabeth Hospital
OL,19,Fbetween 2017 and 2018.
