OL,6,FChristine Blanshard, Chief Medical
OL,7,FOfficer at the Mid and South Essex NHS
OL,8,FFoundation Trust, where Dr Shokouh-
OL,9,FAmiri is now employed, previously
OL,10,Fsaid: "We have confidence that he will
OL,11,Fcontinue to provide high quality, safe
OL,12,Fcare for our patients."
OL,14,FAt the time, a spokesperson added: "We
OL,15,Funderstand the strength of feeling
OL,16,Fabout this case and want to reassure
OL,17,Fwomen that we always have safeguarding
OL,18,Fprocedures in place."
OL,20,FDr Shokouh-Amiri has made a public
OL,21,Fapology for his actions.
